I'm talkin' about.

14:31.938 --> 14:34.572
I've been waiting on this
all day, rainbow. Let's get it.

14:34.574 --> 14:36.941
What's going on downstairs?

14:36.943 --> 14:39.077
Some dude's making dad
act all weird.

14:39.079 --> 14:40.912
White man in a suit?
Leather jacket.

14:40.914 --> 14:42.347
Undercover. Sneaky.

14:42.349 --> 14:45.116
Okay, mr. Tax man,
you want to dance?

14:45.118 --> 14:46.251
We can dance.

14:48.387 --> 14:50.922
This is my take
on collard greens.

14:50.924 --> 14:52.123
Jay: Oh, my goodness!

14:52.125 --> 14:54.058
I love me
some collard green, girl.

14:54.060 --> 14:55.560
Yeah, but they're made
out of kale.

14:55.562 --> 14:57.462
I call them
kale-ard greens.

14:57.464 --> 14:58.963
Stupid full of iron.

14:58.965 --> 14:59.931
Stupid.

14:59.933 --> 15:01.065
Oh, god.

15:01.067 --> 15:02.333
Oh, I also made
mac and cheese.

15:02.335 --> 15:03.935
I love me
some mac and cheese.

15:03.937 --> 15:07.038
But at least I'm gonna be
in the grave smilin'.

15:07.040 --> 15:09.140
Well, nobody's gonna be dying
from my mac and cheese.

15:09.142 --> 15:11.910
Of course it is.
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

15:11.912 --> 15:13.211
You got vegan
mac and cheese?

15:13.213 --> 15:15.146
But aren't the main ingredients
butter and cheese?

15:15.148 --> 15:16.481
Yeah! [ laughs ]

15:16.483 --> 15:19.050
But I used
olive oil and teese.

15:19.052 --> 15:20.518
What?
Teese is like cheese,

15:20.520 --> 15:22.553
But it's actually --
no, no, no.

15:22.555 --> 15:25.123
Jack: Daddy,
check out our costumes.

15:25.125 --> 15:27.058
What the hell
are you two wearing?!

15:27.060 --> 15:28.927
I'm my hero,
sarah palin.

15:28.929 --> 15:31.529
I came within a few votes
of the vice presidency.

15:31.531 --> 15:34.966
I would have won if not for
the liberal "gotcha" media.

15:34.968 --> 15:37.936
My hero's
the godfather of hip-hip --

15:37.938 --> 15:39.170
Vanilla ice.

15:39.172 --> 15:42.707
[<i> vanilla ice's</i>
<i>"ice ice baby" plays</i> ]

15:42.709 --> 15:45.043
Jay:
Yo, you buggin', shorty.

15:45.045 --> 15:46.577
