he is buggin' the hell out.

15:46.579 --> 15:48.179
Yo, don't hurt yourself.
Hey, hey, hey,

15:48.181 --> 15:49.981
Stop this dancing.
Stop this dancing.

15:49.983 --> 15:51.049
Okay, look, go upstairs.

15:51.051 --> 15:53.051
Go upstairs
and change for dinner.

15:53.053 --> 15:54.719
Man, these kids
these days.

15:54.721 --> 15:56.955
My son toby keeps stealing
my car and going joyriding.

15:56.957 --> 15:57.989
He's crazy.

15:57.991 --> 16:01.693
Why don't you cut his foot off
and call him kunta kinte?

16:01.695 --> 16:04.128
Kunta kinte
was about that life.

16:04.130 --> 16:05.964
He was thuggish ruggish
for real, though.

16:05.966 --> 16:08.099
Why are you guys laughing?
That is so brutal.

16:08.101 --> 16:11.069
We're just talking
about "roots," all right?

16:11.071 --> 16:13.304
Oh, yeah, r--
oh, "roots."
yeah, mm-hmm. "roots."

16:13.306 --> 16:15.306
W-well, of course.
[ chuckles ] "roots."

16:15.308 --> 16:18.176
Yeah, I mean,
the kente kunta is, uh...

16:18.178 --> 16:19.310
Very powerful.

16:19.312 --> 16:22.113
That movie was --
I got chills.

16:22.115 --> 16:25.116
You know what's missing
from this moment?

16:25.118 --> 16:26.117
Hot sauce!

16:26.119 --> 16:28.286
Hot sauce
for the mac and teese.

16:28.288 --> 16:30.488
You know, I have a whole case
of it in the pantry.

16:30.490 --> 16:32.523
Baby, come help me get
the case of hot sauce

16:32.525 --> 16:33.591
Out the pantry, please.

16:33.593 --> 16:35.526
[ door closes ]

16:35.528 --> 16:37.362
Oh, good evening, old man.
So good to see you.

16:37.364 --> 16:39.297
Let me apologize
for my tardiness.

16:39.299 --> 16:40.999
I had a meeting
at the gun club

16:41.001 --> 16:43.267
It wasn't
until I was in the prius

16:43.269 --> 16:45.036
And switched it on
that I realized

16:45.038 --> 16:47.071
I had left my attaché case
on the squash court.

16:47.073 --> 16:49.774
So, shall we, um,
get to the business at hand?

16:49.776 --> 16:54.112
I have a little
something-something for you,

16:54.114 --> 16:55.546
As the kids like to say.

16:55.548 --> 16:57.749
I think you'll find
everything to your liking

16:57.751 --> 16:59.117
And in perfect order.

16:59.119 --> 17:00.018
Thanks.

17:00.020 --> 17:01.452
No, no. Thank you.

17:01.454 --> 17:02.553
And good day.

17:02.555 --> 17:04.489
Hey, pops.
What are you doing?

17:04.491 --> 17:06.124
I said,
"good day," sir.

17:10.662 --> 17:13.331
<i>So, my attempt to keep it real</i>
<i>for jay had failed.</i>

17:13.333 --> 17:14.532
<i>And my lesson on "roots"</i>

17:14.534 --> 17:16.434
<i>Wasn't faring much better.</i>
Wait.
Hmm?

17:16.436 --> 17:18.136
Whoa, whoa, whoa,
whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

17:18.138 --> 17:22.407
People have been hounding me
to watch an o.J. Movie?

17:22.409 --> 17:24.542
Where the father
from "brady bunch"

17:24.544 --> 17:25.777
Plays a slave owner?

17:25.779 --> 17:27.078
[ sighs ]

17:27.080 --> 17:30.181
I'm gonna go catch up
on my "empires."

17:30.183 --> 17:32.083
[ sighs ]

17:32.085 --> 17:34.519
What you sittin' around with
your head droopin' down for?

17:34.521 --> 17:36.821
You didn't try to bribe
the wrong white guy.

17:36.823 --> 17:39.123
Pops, my career is over.

17:39.125 --> 17:42.293
I'm about to lose this account
to charlie.

17:42.295 --> 17:44.128
He lives in his car.

17:44.130 --> 17:45.663
He put a humidifier in it.

17:45.665 --> 17:46.831
Listen to me, son.

17:46.833 --> 17:48.299
Don't let some white man
convince you

17:48.301 --> 17:50.068
That your ability
to move between both worlds

17:50.070 --> 17:51.602
Is something
you shouldn't be proud of.

17:51.604 --> 17:54.806
Being able to switch it up
is a necessity.

17:54.808 --> 17:56.307
And the way you do it --

17:56.309 --> 17:58.376
Smooth, son, smooth,
like a superhero.

17:58.378 --> 17:59.844
I mean,
I'm almost jealous.

17:59.846 --> 18:01.679
How much of my scotch
have you had?

18:01.681 --> 18:04.082
Look, all I'm saying is
being able to switch it up

18:04.084 --> 18:05.817
Has gotten you
some nice things --

18:05.819 --> 18:08.820
This house, your wife,
this scotch.

18:08.822 --> 18:10.621
By the way, you're out.

18:10.623 --> 18:12.757
Ahh.
But I got to tell you.

18:12.759 --> 18:14.826
The thing I'm probably
the most proud of you for is --

18:14.828 --> 18:16.861
[ cellphone beeps, vibrates ]
oh, hold that thought.

18:16.863 --> 18:18.396
Yep, that's my uber.

18:18.398 --> 18:19.630
Got to go, son.

18:19.632 --> 18:21.365
You probably won't be seeing me
for a while,

18:21.367 --> 18:23.101
At least not until
this tax thing blows over.

18:23.103 --> 18:24.769
And I would give you
a forwarding address,

18:24.771 --> 18:26.537
But you liable to tell
the white man anything.

18:26.539 --> 18:28.539
Blessing and a curse, son.
Blessing and a curse.

18:28.541 --> 18:32.176
<i>Despite pops'</i>
<i>wesley snipes-ian understanding</i>

18:32.178 --> 18:35.146
<i>Of american tax law,</i>
<i>he was right.</i>

18:35.148 --> 18:37.882
<i>How did white jay</i>
<i>make me feel bad</i>

18:37.884 --> 18:41.853
<i>About being a successful</i>
<i>black man?</i>

18:41.855 --> 18:43.855
So, uh, these are bushes,

18:43.857 --> 18:46.791
Which is a great place where
you can hide your packages.

18:46.793 --> 18:49.127
Also, you can hide
your packages,

18:49.129 --> 18:51.529
Uh, here or...

18:51.531 --> 18:52.597
Here...

18:52.599 --> 18:54.265
Or one of my favorites...

18:54.267 --> 18:56.134
Uh, here.

18:56.136 --> 18:59.403
Hey, look.
Uh, I'm sorry to interrupt.

18:59.405 --> 19:01.606
Charlie, you can stop.
Look, the account is his.

19:01.608 --> 19:03.808
Dre, what are you doing?
All week, I've been listening

19:03.810 --> 19:05.843
To the white cornel west
over there

19:05.845 --> 19:09.714
Make me feel like I wasn't
black enough for this campaign.

19:09.716 --> 19:11.682
You know what?
Screw you.

19:11.684 --> 19:12.850
Okay. You know what?

19:12.852 --> 19:14.752
Dre, that is not
a closer move.

19:14.754 --> 19:18.589
Keepin' it real
isn't some checklist you find

19:18.591 --> 19:19.891
On "yo! Mtv raps."

19:19.893 --> 19:22.860
It's about being you,
and for me,

19:22.862 --> 19:25.863
Sometimes that mean watching
"the good wife" with the missus

19:25.865 --> 19:28.266
While we eat mac and teese,
all right?

19:28.268 --> 19:30.835
It's got my cholesterol down.
I'm off the lipitor, son.

19:30.837 --> 19:34.438
Dre, you know, I really --
I really don't think --

19:34.440 --> 19:35.873
Jay: Yes. Yes, yes.
[ claps ]

19:35.875 --> 19:37.508
This is what I wanted
to see.

19:37.510 --> 19:39.810
This is the dre johnson
I've heard so much about.

19:39.812 --> 19:41.479
You've been
walking around here

19:41.481 --> 19:45.316
