of that swag you're famous for.

19:45.318 --> 19:46.851
Okay.
So, what are you saying?

19:46.853 --> 19:48.686
I want you to head up
this account.

19:48.688 --> 19:50.855
Do you? Hmm.

19:50.857 --> 19:53.691
Beg me.
Nah, I ain't doin' that,
playboy.

19:53.693 --> 19:54.926
I will.

19:54.928 --> 19:56.794
Please, dre,
take the account.

19:56.796 --> 19:57.962
Please.

19:57.964 --> 19:59.597
My back
is against the wall.

19:59.599 --> 20:00.831
Ch-charlie, I got you.

20:01.934 --> 20:04.502
All right.
I'll take it.

20:04.504 --> 20:08.239
Just make this is the guy
that shows up to work every day.

20:08.241 --> 20:09.907
All day, every day.

20:09.909 --> 20:12.343
100% uncut dre.

20:12.345 --> 20:15.313
"the white cornel west" --
I like that.

20:15.315 --> 20:18.316
Uh, do you want me
to finish?

20:18.318 --> 20:19.584
'cause me and laura,

20:19.586 --> 20:21.485
We was up late
putting this together.

20:21.487 --> 20:23.421
Like, you'll never find one
here.

20:23.423 --> 20:25.323
Uh, decoy boxes
could be awesome.

20:25.325 --> 20:26.457
Ooh, how about a wig?

20:29.695 --> 20:31.629
Hey, pops.

20:31.631 --> 20:32.763
What are you doing back?

20:32.765 --> 20:33.664
Pops: Oh, uh...

20:33.666 --> 20:37.835
If anyone comes looking for me,
