Was only sending someone here

20:42.875 --> 20:46.877
As courtesy because you are
on their senior citizen's list.

20:46.879 --> 20:49.347
They only want a copy
of the sales receipt
of your old lincoln.

20:49.349 --> 20:51.482
Your mama took that lincoln
from me in the divorce --

20:51.484 --> 20:52.850
Out of pure spite,
I might add.

20:52.852 --> 20:55.920
That means I didn't sell it --
she did.

20:55.922 --> 20:58.289
They're not looking for me.
They're looking for her.
Okay.

20:58.291 --> 20:59.490
Oh, my goodness.

20:59.492 --> 21:02.360
The I.R.S.
Is finally going to do for me

21:02.362 --> 21:04.929
What I was never able to do
for myself.

21:04.931 --> 21:06.964
What?
Bury her.

21:06.966 --> 21:08.866
I love this country.

21:08.868 --> 21:10.901
Hey, pops,
I hope this little scare

21:10.903 --> 21:13.871
Has taught you a lesson
in fiscal responsibility.

21:13.873 --> 21:15.306
Oh, yes.

21:15.308 --> 21:17.575
I am...Untouchable.

21:17.577 --> 21:20.611
If anyone comes looking for me,
you know where I'll be.

21:20.613 --> 21:21.912
At the track.
At the track.

21:21.914 --> 21:23.047
Yeah.
